{"tid":265456,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[民主黨又賣香港]啟德319億撥款　18票比17票僅通過","createTime":"2017-05-31T15:37:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T15:45:35.000Z","uid":96964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7115a8aeecb0abd67397fb929124a28d4127cbf4","tid":265456,"uid":96964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T15:37:47.000Z","msg":"立法會工務小組經過逾12小時會議討論啟德體育園的319億撥款申請後，今早正式進行表決。由於政府首次提出「提案誘因」招標，<span style=\"color: red;\">令投標者落選後，仍可取得6,000萬元或擬備標書實際費用的一半</span>，以此吸引承辦商投標，做法引起爭議。<br />\n<br />\n多名泛民議員提交修訂案，但全被否決。有關撥款最終在18名建制派投贊成票、17名民主派議員投反對票下，議案僅僅獲得通過。由於形勢緊張，當投票結果顯示時，有人大聲呼叫，問：「 黃碧雲喺邊 ？」。議案預料下月交到財委會審議。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">民主派共有20人是工務小組委員，民主黨黃碧雲、尹兆堅，以及資訊科技界莫乃光並未現身。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母民主黨"},{"pid":"c1a61b2b442fd9d1f0e54f8722923274b9cea84f","tid":265456,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T15:38:39.000Z","msg":"民主黨 _ _ _ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67d88d87058ed6a583afd4451e2c7df567d6bbcd","tid":265456,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T15:40:28.000Z","msg":"民主黨賣香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2267a7b15e92df3039d636e377e658c2d62dc00f","tid":265456,"uid":96964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T15:45:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170531&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=56763408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170531%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D56763408&d=sUc5KZ8H5SHklGhWMu8F%2B2xr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=9bb5065b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20170531%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D56763408&h=13ee9274\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20170531&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=56763408</a><br />\n政府堅持設提案誘因 啟德體育園319億撥款一票之差獲批<